==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɔɪ|-ɔɪ]]

===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# To [[give]] [[someone]] [[work]] or a [[job]].
# To [[put]] [[something]] into [[use]] or [[service]]; to [[make use of]].
#:''How do you '''employ''' your spare time?''

